          <p className="text-zinc-300 mb-4">Think of churn as a temperature gauge. Your Superfans are boiling — hot engagement, high frequency, deep interactions. Your Churned followers are frozen. The At-Risk segment is lukewarm and cooling fast. Your job is to detect the cooling before it reaches freezing point, and apply targeted heat (the right content, at the right time, in the right format) to reverse the trend.</p>

